      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(minimax): request hex TTS output explicitly",
        "body": "## Summary\n- send \\`output_format: \"hex\"\\` in MiniMax TTS requests\n- send \\`stream: false\\` explicitly for the non-streaming path\n- extend the MiniMax speech-provider test to lock the request shape\n\n## Why\nThe MiniMax provider decodes \\`data.audio\\` as hex, but the request did not explicitly ask the API for hex output. This makes the integration brittle and can break TTS/voice-note generation depending on API defaults.\n\n## Proof\n\n### Source-level evidence (no live credentials needed)\n\n**Current main — request shape (extensions/minimax/tts.ts):**\n\\`\\`\\`typescript\nbody: JSON.stringify({\n  model,\n  text,\n  voice_setting: { voice_id: voiceId, speed, vol, pitch },\n  audio_setting: { format, sample_rate },\n  // NO stream: false\n  // NO output_format: \"hex\"\n}),\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n**Current main — response decode (same file):**\n\\`\\`\\`typescript\nconst hexAudio = body?.data?.audio;\nreturn Buffer.from(hexAudio, \"hex\"); // assumes hex without requesting it\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n**The fix adds the missing fields:**\n\\`\\`\\`typescript\nbody: JSON.stringify({\n  model,\n  text,\n  stream: false,        // ← added\n  output_format: \"hex\", // ← added\n  voice_setting: { voice_id: voiceId, speed, vol, pitch },\n  audio_setting: { format, sample_rate },\n}),\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n**Test assertion (extensions/minimax/speech-provider.test.ts):**\n\\`\\`\\`typescript\nexpect(body.stream).toBe(false);\nexpect(body.output_format).toBe(\"hex\");\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n### Why this matters\nThe MiniMax T2A API defaults to streaming audio. The plugin unconditionally decodes \\`data.audio\\` as hex. If the API ever changed its default output format, TTS would break silently. Making the contract explicit prevents this.\n\n## Tests\n\\`pnpm vitest run extensions/minimax/speech-provider.test.ts\\` ✅ (33/33)\n\n## Rebase\nRebased onto current main (07dfdd4bd0). No conflicts beyond resolved test assertion style.",
